comments: Howard (LAL) establishes his screening position in Brogdon's (IND) path and absorbs the contact.
Caldwell-Pope (LAL) does not step out of bounds.
Howard (LAL) and Turner (IND) briefly engage and disengage in the post off ball.
James (LAL) slightly extends his leg into Holiday's (IND) path, but does not affect his ability to defend.
Warren (IND) makes contact to Davis' (LAL) head and affects his shot near the rim.
Holiday (IND) establishes his screening position in Davis' (LAL) path and absorbs the contact.
Davis (LAL) moves parallel alongside Warren's (IND) path to the basket and absorbs the contact on his driving shot attempt.
James (LAL) braces for the oncoming contact with a bent forearm from Holiday (IND) but does not deliver contact.
Turner (IND) engages and disengages with Howard (LAL) during the rebound.
Warren (IND) extends his hand forward and delivers contact to Davis (LAL) that affects his ability to defend.
Turner (IND) makes incidental foot contact with Davis' (LAL) foot during the pick.
Davis (LAL) briefly places his arm around Warren's (IND) hip before correcting during the screen.
Caruso (LAL) makes hand on ball contact to dislodge the ball away from Turner (IND) during the rebound.
Turner (IND) sets the pick on James (LAL), but does not deliver contact.
James (LAL) makes marginal contact to Brogdon's (IND) front off ball.
Holiday (IND) establishes position inbounds prior to making contact to the ball.
James (LAL) commits a take foul on Holiday (IND).
Kuzma (LAL) commits a take foul on Oladipo (IND).
